snippet.title: Haven Moon - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
-- Please now refer to my personal channel for official Haven Moon Videos --
http://youtube.com/channel/UCp0D4ADMG2O_8l7QzgEH-AA


Haven Moon will transport you to a mysterious world where you will have to explore abandoned islands and solve their secrets to find a treasure. In this Myst-like game inspired by Jules Verne’s universe, use your senses and intelligence to find your way through secret passages and curious machinery.

Available on Steam :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/493720/

Twitter :
https://twitter.com/roussel_fr


Created by François Roussel - Original music by Leo J. Russlan
